com.planet_ink.coffee_mud.Areas.interfaces

Interface AutoGenArea

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Affectable, Area, Behavable, java.lang.Cloneable, CMObject, java.lang.Comparable<CMObject>, Contingent, Economics, Environmental, Modifiable, MsgListener, Physical, PhysicalAgent, Places, StatsAffecting, Tickable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StdAutoGenInstance

    public interface AutoGenArea
extends Area
    AutoGenAreas are areas that utilize the random area generation system (percolator) to generate their rooms. As such, the common parameters for the auto gen system are herein exposed
    Author:
    Bo Zimmerman
